Besides, I should have gone to that unhappy man all the same as I thought him in danger of death.
â
Brother Archangias, his mouth full, struck the table violently with his knife, and roared: âJeanbernat is a dog; he ought to die like a dog.
â Then seeing the priest about to protest he cut him short: âNo, no, for him there is no God, no penitence, no mercy.
