âMonsieur Caffin used to tell me everything,â she moaned out.
However, she soon grew calmer.
Brother Archangias was finishing a big piece of cheese, apparently quite unruffled by the scene.
In his opinion Abbe Mouret really needed being kept straight, and La Teuse was right in making him feel the reins.
