She declared that she had never done so; but all at once she seemed to change her mind, and allowed herself to be convinced.
However, that did not prevent her from finishing her tale in these words: âWhen the lord went away his hair was quite white.
He had all the gates barricaded up, so that no one might get inside and disturb the lady.
