That evening La Teuse felt so cross that she had talked of going to bed as soon as the cloth was removed.
The Brother, however, wanted his game of cards.
So he caught hold of her shoulders and sat her down, so roughly that the chair creaked beneath her.
And forthwith he began to shuffle the cards.
