But she laughed at him.
âDonât talk any of your nonsense to me, my man!
Donât you know that it is forbidden you to lay your hands upon a woman, just as itâs forbidden for a donkey to have anything to do with the _Pater Noster_?
Just you try to strangle me and youâll see what Iâll do!
But do be quiet now, and let us finish the game.
See, hereâs another king.
