But the Brother, holding up a card, went on growling:
âShe must have come by some road that the devil alone knows for me to have missed her to-day.
Every afternoon I go and keep guard up yonder by the Paradou.
If ever I find them together again, I will acquaint the hussy with a stout dogwood stick which I have cut expressly for her benefit.
And I shall keep a watch in the church as well now.
